results.query: Select B.ID, B.Text, B.Lemma, B.POS, B.Book, B.Chapter, B.Verse, A.MarkRef, A.LukeRef, Case when A.M = 1 then 'M' when A.A = 1 then 'A' when A.C = 1 then 'C' when A.T = 1 then 'T' else '' end as TMatch, Case when A.M1 = 1 then 'M1' when A.A1 = 1 then 'A1' when A.C1 = 1 then 'C1' when A.T1 = 1 then 'T1' else '' end as LMatch, A.M, A.A, A.C, A.T, A.M1, A.A1, A.C1, A.T1, A.newVs from MattColors A left join (Select ID, Text, Lemma, POS, Book, Chapter, Verse from Gospels) B on A.ID = B.ID where chapter = 9 and verse between 1 and 8
